<h2>Hi <%= @contact.name.split.first %>,</h2>

<p>Thanks for reaching out! I've received your message and will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>

<div style="margin: 24px 0; padding: 16px; background: #f5f5f5; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;">
  <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #666;">Your message:</p>
  <p style="margin: 0; white-space: pre-wrap;"><%= @contact.message %></p>
</div>

<p>In the meantime, feel free to check out my latest work on my portfolio.</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br>
  <%= @profile&.full_name || "Wintan" %>
</p>
